<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="232" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,289,640]" pageId="5" pageNumber="232">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,434,460]" pageId="5" pageNumber="232">Remarks.</emphasis>
When established this subgenus, three species of 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Bey-Bienko" baseAuthorityYear="1933" box="[874,1035,434,460]" class="Insecta" family="Haglotettigoniidae" genus="Modicogryllus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="232" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bucharicus">
<emphasis box="[874,1035,434,460]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="232">M. bucharicus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName box="[1050,1210,434,460]" class="Insecta" family="Haglotettigoniidae" genus="Modicogryllus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="232" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="confirmata">
<emphasis box="[1050,1210,434,460]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="232">M. confirmata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Chopard" authorityYear="1961" box="[1264,1375,434,460]" class="Insecta" family="Haglotettigoniidae" genus="Modicogryllus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="232" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ehsani">
<emphasis box="[1264,1375,434,460]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="232">M. ehsani</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
were included in the taxon. But the 
<typeStatus box="[483,531,470,496]" pageId="5" pageNumber="232">type</typeStatus>
species, 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Bey-Bienko" baseAuthorityYear="1933" box="[631,792,470,496]" class="Insecta" family="Haglotettigoniidae" genus="Modicogryllus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="232" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bucharicus">
<emphasis box="[631,792,470,496]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="232">M. bucharicus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, bears a genitalia complex distinguished from the remain- der ones and the form of it is very similar to the species of 
<taxonomicName authorityName=", Gorochov" authorityYear="1986" box="[835,1026,506,532]" class="Insecta" family="Haglotettigoniidae" genus="Eumodicogryllus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="232" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[835,1026,506,532]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="232">Eumodicogryllus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, which was arranged as a subgenus of 
<taxonomicName authority="(Gorochov, 1986)" baseAuthorityName="Gorochov" baseAuthorityYear="1986" box="[184,557,542,569]" class="Insecta" family="Haglotettigoniidae" genus="Modicogryllus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="232" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[184,347,542,568]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="232">Modicogryllus</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Gorochov, A. V." box="[363,548,542,569]" pageId="5" pageNumber="232" pagination="3 - 15" refId="ref14109" refString="Gorochov, A. V. (1986) New and little known Grylloidea (Orthoptera) from Middle Asia and adjacent territories. Proceedings of Zoological Institute of Academy of Sciences of USSR, 140, 3 - 15." type="journal article" year="1986">Gorochov, 1986</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
and was subsequently upgraded to a genus (
<bibRefCitation author="Defaut, B." box="[1070,1224,542,568]" pageId="5" pageNumber="232" pagination="107 - 112" refId="ref13913" refString="Defaut, B. (2001) Actualisation taxonomique et nomenclaturale du &lt;synopsis des orthopteres de france&gt;. Materiaux Entomocenotiques, 6, 107 - 112." type="journal article" year="2001">Defaut, 2001</bibRefCitation>
). According to the features of the genitalia of 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Walker" baseAuthorityYear="1859" box="[447,618,578,604]" class="Insecta" family="Haglotettigoniidae" genus="Modicogryllus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="232" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="confirmatus">
<emphasis box="[447,618,578,604]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="232">M. confirmatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Chopard" authorityYear="1961" box="[670,779,578,604]" class="Insecta" family="Haglotettigoniidae" genus="Modicogryllus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="232" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ehsani">
<emphasis box="[670,779,578,604]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="232">M. ehsani</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, we considered that the total of nine species as listed above should be arranged into this subgenus.
</paragraph>
